messages.message: Hi team -- In next week's AI Hub push, there will be a setting icon appears next to a converse or build project to let the user turn on table extraction and multi-step question answering. The setting icon & everything under it is *internal user only* -- setting will only show up for users with a `@instabase.com` account. We'd love your feedback! But please note that these features are not ready for any external users.
